Operations

findUnique

Find zero or one ProductType

// Get one ProductType
const productType = await prisma.productType.findUnique({
  where: {
    // ... provide filter here
  }
})

Input

Name Type Required
where ProductTypeWhereUniqueInput Yes

Output

Type: ProductType
Required: No
List: No

findFirst

Find first ProductType

// Get one ProductType
const productType = await prisma.productType.findFirst({
  where: {
    // ... provide filter here
  }
})

Input

Name Type Required
where ProductTypeWhereInput No
orderBy ProductTypeOrderByWithRelationInput[] | ProductTypeOrderByWithRelationInput No
cursor ProductTypeWhereUniqueInput No
take Int No
skip Int No
distinct ProductTypeScalarFieldEnum | ProductTypeScalarFieldEnum[] No

Output

Type: ProductType
Required: No
List: No

findMany

Find zero or more ProductType

// Get all ProductType
const ProductType = await prisma.productType.findMany()
// Get first 10 ProductType
const ProductType = await prisma.productType.findMany({ take: 10 })

Input

Name Type Required
where ProductTypeWhereInput No
orderBy ProductTypeOrderByWithRelationInput[] | ProductTypeOrderByWithRelationInput No
cursor ProductTypeWhereUniqueInput No
